  <thing id="rcuWtcFrsF" name="Frostfoot" description="This ability works like the {i}spider climb{/i} spell, but the surfaces the witch climbs must be icy. The witch can move across icy surfaces without penalty and does not need to make Acrobatics checks to run or charge on ice. She can move across regular snow without penalty, and heavy snow only costs her 2 squares of movement instead of 4." compset="RaceCustom" summary="As {i}spider climb{/i}, but only on icy surfaces.">
